<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="forgive-and-forget">forgive and forget</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不念旧恶；不记仇：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is a virtue to forgive and forget, especially in such a competitive and stressful society.
不记仇是一种美德，特别是在这样一个竞争激烈、有压力的社会中。</p><footer>2012 江苏书面表达改</footer></div></div>